Class MultiComposite<BDO extends DataObject,X extends Composite<BDO,X>>

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Contexed, TableStructureContributer<BDO>

    public abstract class MultiComposite<BDO extends DataObject,X extends Composite<BDO,X>>
extends Composite<BDO,X>
    An abstract base class for a Composite that combines multiple Composites of the same type. Each nested Composite adds its own fields to the parent factory.
